Description:
2x8x400, 45” between reps, 3’ between sets. Pace was 80s and I did that + & - based on wind/effort. I’m confused by how I get fit off workouts like this LOL but I’ll do whatever works and this type of stuff apparently does haha. 

Not gonna lie when it was raining I started thinking about how I could have been in Paris rn instead of running back and forth on this path- but will take it day by day to heal the ❤️‍🩹

Made up my own aqua jog workout to pass time: 

warm up + cool down and then, 7-5-4-3-2-1-45-1-45-30-45-30-15-30-15 and then 3x2mins to flush the legs lmao byeeee
